Academic References
-------------------
The LoRa PHY algorithms in this project are based on the work of:

  Joachim Tapparel and Andreas Burg
  Telecommunications Circuits Laboratory (TCL)
  École Polytechnique Fédérale de Lausanne (EPFL)

  "Design and Implementation of a LoRa PHY Transceiver for IoT Using GNU Radio"
  GRCon 2024

  Reference implementation: gr-lora_sdr
  https://github.com/tapparelj/gr-lora_sdr
  License: GPL-3.0

The whitening LFSR sequence was independently derived from the specification in:

  Pieter Robyns, Peter Quax, Wim Lamotte, and William Thenaers
  "A Multi-Channel Software Decoder for the LoRa Modulation Scheme"
  Hasselt University, 2017

